{"tid":855319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綠色和平：可口可樂是塑膠垃圾頭號製造者","createTime":"2018-10-10T03:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T08:53:53.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"557ff898db5d0a9453a4e9a9af131d9c72ccdf6f","tid":855319,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/10/98/5375484.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F98%2F5375484.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=a165f353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環保團體綠色和平組織（Greenpeace）在布達佩斯的英雄廣場舉行塑料廢物示威遊行。路透社<br />\n<br />\n環保團體綠色和平組織（Greenpeace）今天說，可口可樂公司（Coca-ColaCo.）、百事公司（PepsiCo）和雀巢公司（Nestle）等飲料公司，經查是世界上最大的塑膠垃圾製造者。<br />\n和「擺脫塑膠」（Break Free From Plastic）運動合作，綠色和平組織表示，他們在世界上42個國家執行239次清除塑膠垃圾行動，共撿到18萬7000件塑膠垃圾。此舉目的在瞭解大型企業如何加劇汙染問題。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平說，全世界最大軟性飲料製造商可口可樂公司是頭號塑膠垃圾來源。在42國當中，有40國發現可口可樂公司品牌的塑膠垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n「擺脫塑膠」全球統籌者赫南德茲（VonHernandez）說：「做這樣的品牌清算，提供無法否認的證據，呈現大型企業在全球塑膠汙染無止境危機中所扮演的角色。」<br />\n<br />\n整體而言，最普遍的塑膠垃圾是「聚苯乙烯」，這是包裝和塑料咖啡杯的材料；「聚乙烯對苯二甲酸酯」（PET）緊追在後，常見產品是寶特瓶和容器等。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂公司發言人發布聲明說：「我們與綠色和平目標一致，志在消除海洋裡的垃圾，並已準備好要盡我們的責任，協助解決此一重大挑戰。」可口可樂公司已承諾在2030年前收集並回收其所賣出的每個瓶子與罐子。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂公司、百事公司和雀巢公司都已承諾在2025年更換包裝。可口可樂說，所有包裝都將是可回收材料；雀巢說，將採可回收或可再利用的包裝；百事公司說，將採可回收、可作為堆肥或可生物分解包裝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3413587?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F3413587%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=TMeNIT5X4VpCfFkda38KslzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=6476c6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3413587?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"da3fcb35396cd4d7f9be1d7aba9f78f70beab22a","tid":855319,"uid":3765,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"環保閪真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"a7a3fb1aa6a2d9aee612ec26ae96171f304ca5f4","tid":855319,"uid":78971,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"因為佢大啫<br />\n又唔係有心用得多"},{"pid":"338daa6328e769a3a8e48e6d76013176556c6206","tid":855319,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a7a3fb1aa6a2d9aee612ec26ae96171f304ca5f4","tid":855319,"uid":78971,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"因為佢大啫<br />\n又唔係有心用得多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"一雞死一雞鳴...<br />\n<br />\n環保撚走去怪責可口可樂"},{"pid":"fe995ebab338148ca5fe9bdd11e542b06c78e89e","tid":855319,"uid":153258,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"都痴撚線<br />\n收左錢整跌股價？"},{"pid":"b3b5c65673d2421036c3154f0cd796fa53b249ef","tid":855319,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"自己拎個杯去超市買可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c0465212f5f8ccd1e2a15b4728cadeaee69050","tid":855319,"uid":80598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b3b5c65673d2421036c3154f0cd796fa53b249ef","tid":855319,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"自己拎個杯去超市買可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"幫我倒落個口度得喇"},{"pid":"f4f17c3122bb16082537516213830d005095dc3e","tid":855319,"uid":35908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"百事可樂抬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d593e666b74331bc4005e19899f7e9dc78fe2e69","tid":855319,"uid":39365,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"人口越多垃圾就越多, 真正減廢就要減少人口, 否則根本無用"},{"pid":"38844c65d9f074531e5ade42a0b73ba7ae41f1dc